sub_title: Translator | Journalist | Podcaster | Copywriter | Swedish language consultant at Self-employed
summary: Language nerd and communications specialist with over fifteen years’ professional experience working with news media and languages in different ways - I write, research, translate, revise, edit, assess quality and provide general language consultancy services for Swedish targets. Fluent speaker of English and French.  Co-host, co-producer and editor of local feature news podcast Sounding Out Horsham. Quality focused believer of real news and hard facts with an analytical mind and a genuine interest in people and words. Freelance enthusiast and a big supporter of alternative lifestyles and worklives - always open for new work collaborations! Member of CIOL and SFÖ.
